<th>Photon polarization Bob measures</th>
<td width="40pt"><a href="/wiki/File:Arrow_north.svg" class="image" title="Arrow north.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Arrow_north.svg/8px-Arrow_north.svg.png" width="8" height="20" border="0" /></a></td>
