<li>Original paper on the BB84 Protocol for Quantum Cryptography<a href="http://quantum.bbn.com/dscgi/ds.py/Get/File-18/BB84.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://quantum.bbn.com/dscgi/ds.py/Get/File-18/BB84.pdf" rel="nofollow">[12]</a></li>
<li>Original paper on Entanglement-based quantum cryptography <a href="http://quantum.bbn.com/dscgi/ds.py/Get/File-369/Ekert_-_QKD_Based_On_Bells_Theorem.pdf" class="external autonumber" title="http://quantum.bbn.com/dscgi/ds.py/Get/File-369/Ekert_-_QKD_Based_On_Bells_Theorem.pdf" rel="nofollow">[13]</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
